    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a simplified model consisting of abstract objects, their attributes, and their operations that is independent of encoding and transport.  This document also addresses security, internationalization, and directory issues.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
